OL,3,CMendy 'struggled to pay child support'
OL,4,Cafter Man City stopped wages
OL,6,FBenjamin Mendy "struggled to pay child
OL,7,Fsupport" when Manchester City stopped
OL,8,Fpaying him after he was charged with
OL,9,Frape and sexual assault, an employment
OL,10,Ftribunal has heard.
OL,12,FFootballers Raheem Sterling, Bernardo
OL,13,FSilva and Riyad Mahrez lent money to
OL,14,Fthe French international, who now
OL,15,Fclaims to be owed #11.5million in
OL,16,Funpaid wages.
OL,18,FThe 30-year-old former City player's
OL,19,F#500,000 per month wage was withheld
OL,20,Fby the club after he was charged in
OL,21,F2021, the tribunal was told.
