OL,6,FMendy, appearing via videolink, told
OL,7,Fthe tribunal he and his agent N'diaye
OL,8,Fhad been assured by City's then chief
OL,9,Ffootball operating officer Omar
OL,10,FBerrada that he would receive his
OL,11,Funpaid wages once he had been cleared
OL,12,Fof the charges.
OL,14,FThe footballer sent Berrada a WhatsApp
OL,15,Fmessage in November 2022, asking if he
OL,16,Fcould confirm in writing that the
OL,17,Fwages would be paid, the tribunal
OL,18,Fheard.
